Manketsi Mamoabi Emily Tlhape bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa bụ onye otu African National Congress (ANC) nke National Assembly of South Africa kemgbe 2019.
Tlhape jere ozi dị ka onye otu Executive Council (MEC) na gọọmentị mpaghara North West
N'ọnwa Disemba afọ 2018, onye isi ala Job Mokgoro chụpụrụ ya dị ka MEC n'ihi akụkọ na ọ zuru ehi maka ndị ọrụ ugbo na-apụta.
A họpụtara Tlhape ka ọ bụrụ onye omebe iwu mba site na ndepụta mba ANC na ntuli aka 2019.
